{"tid":822312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝笑鳩山竹個風冇料到個堆人柒唔柒D","createTime":"2018-09-16T09:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T10:08:02.000Z","uid":96694,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e3a52db05720ca56296fa9e2f245e988ae4af3","tid":822312,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"香港有史以來面對最勁既超強颱風<br />\n唔少地方都塌樹  就連地盤都塌<br />\n好多地方都爆哂玻璃<br />\n嚴重既水浸<br />\n根據香港天文台數據資料顯示<br />\n大澳既海水高度上漲到海圖基準面以上約<span style=\"color: red;\">3.8米</span><br />\n維港上漲到海圖基準面以上約<span style=\"color: red;\">3.9米</span><br />\n而尖鼻咀更加上漲到海圖基準面以上約<span style=\"color: red;\">4.0米</span><br />\n教育部頭先都宣布埋聽日所有學校停課<br />\n係香港中學牛小學雞夢寐以求既放假<br />\n聽日冇風打都停課<br />\n就知今次個風對香港造成左幾大影響"},{"pid":"886edfe9e52191c0e1e7cdfbac811046325f1c3b","tid":822312,"uid":8175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"c566787a815d2119d5b4f2e49d662b1a7c9b7ce9","tid":822312,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"c6303307b830849037c2e6dd658d529c5ca92937","tid":822312,"uid":120462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0083ee3b17af4b2df884e9132b515e91825aa61a","tid":822312,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b16e2a3fbdfa7276bc1c067477404cc1a05aa58","tid":822312,"uid":10210,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"波台班垃圾不嬲柒架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111c73769a94fcbb99f8ef30dd5589c0b145adf9","tid":822312,"uid":194785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"0247aab711e8bbc663d5ff99bf65a94451813d10","tid":822312,"uid":111271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"班垃圾就好